//! Fano runtime kernel.
//!
//! This is the executable shadow of `Gnosis.FanoIncidence`: the full Triton
//! carrier is the three-bit cube, `000` is the root/god position, visible Fano
//! points are `001..111`, and collision is XOR.
//!
//! The module intentionally stays at the routing layer. It does not claim that
//! arbitrary Grassmannian arithmetic, floating-point residual math, Plucker
//! signs, or positivity have been reduced to XOR. Callers must enter through a
//! projection/adapter that proves the operation being routed preserves this
//! binary projective shadow.

